# Fichier d'exemples de requêtes API pour Glucosen Backend
# À utiliser avec Postman, REST Client (VS Code) ou cURL

### ==========================================
### 1. AUTHENTIFICATION
### ==========================================

### 1.1 Register (Créer un compte)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-15"
}

### 1.2 Login (Se connecter)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123"
}

### 1.3 Get Profile (Obtenir le profil)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### 1.4 Update Profile (Mettre à jour le profil)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jonathan",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-15"
}

### ==========================================
### 2. GLUCOSE
### ==========================================

### 2.1 Create Glucose Reading (Créer une lecture)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/glucose
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "glucoseLevel": 145,
  "readingTime": "2026-03-29T10:30:00Z",
  "unit": "mg/dL",
  "notes": "Avant le petit-déjeuner"
}

### 2.2 Get All Glucose Readings (Obtenir toutes les lectures)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/glucose?limit=30&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### 2.3 Get Glucose by Date Range (Par période)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/glucose/range?startDate=2026-03-01&endDate=2026-03-31
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### 2.4 Get Glucose Statistics (Statistiques)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/glucose/statistics?days=30
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### 2.5 Update Glucose Reading (Mettre à jour une lecture)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/glucose/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "glucoseLevel": 150,
  "readingTime": "2026-03-29T10:30:00Z",
  "notes": "Après le petit-déjeuner"
}

### 2.6 Delete Glucose Reading (Supprimer une lecture)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/glucose/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

