POST http://localhost:3000/api/meals
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mealType": "breakfast",
  "mealTime": "2026-03-29T08:00:00Z",
  "description": "Oeufs brouillés, pain grillé et confiture",
  "carbs": 45,
  "protein": 15,
  "fat": 12,
  "calories": 350
}

### 3.2 Get All Meals (Obtenir tous les repas)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/meals?limit=30&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### 3.3 Get Meals by Date Range (Par période)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/meals/range?startDate=2026-03-01&endDate=2026-03-31
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### 3.4 Update Meal (Mettre à jour un repas)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/meals/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mealType": "breakfast",
  "carbs": 50,
  "protein": 18
}

### 3.5 Delete Meal (Supprimer un repas)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/meals/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### ==========================================
### 4. INSULINE
### ==========================================

### 4.1 Create Insulin Log (Créer un journal d'insuline)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/insulin
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "insulinType": "Humalog",
  "units": 10,
  "administrationTime": "2026-03-29T08:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Avant le petit-déjeuner"
}

### 4.2 Get All Insulin Logs (Obtenir tous les journaux)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/insulin?limit=30&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### 4.3 Get Insulin Logs by Date Range (Par période)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/insulin/range?startDate=2026-03-01&endDate=2026-03-31
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### 4.4 Get Total Daily Insulin Units (Total quotidien)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/insulin/daily-total?date=2026-03-29
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### 4.5 Update Insulin Log (Mettre à jour un journal)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/insulin/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "units": 12,
  "notes": "Dosage augmenté"
}

### 4.6 Delete Insulin Log (Supprimer un journal)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/insulin/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

